{"data":[{"date":"07:37 19/07","title":"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Real Madrid h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/chu-tich-real-madrid-hua-se-no-bom-tan-khoa-lap-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Florentino Perez kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid s\u1ebd t\u00edch c\u1ef1c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i s\u1ed1ng Cristiano Ronaldo.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mua Hazard thay Ronaldo?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 2018, Cristiano Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 vinh quang \u1edf Bernabeu nh\u1eb1m t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi \u1edf m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd khi \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid h\u00e8 2018 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n sau CR7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid h\u00e8 2018 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n sau CR7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-Madrid-he-2018-hua-hen-se-no-bom-tan-sau-CR7-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid h\u00e8 2018 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n sau khi chia tay si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eafm vai ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 g\u1ea7n th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 \u0111\u00e3 qua, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh Los Blancos ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd b\u1ecb suy gi\u1ea3m \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u, \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi CLB ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha ph\u1ea3i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c b\u1ea1o chi h\u01a1n sau nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c bom t\u1ea5n, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn \u0111\u00e3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng vang d\u1ed9i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u1eddi h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n, cam \u0111oan c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u00fd th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o Real Madrid trong m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.\u201d \u2013 Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng trong l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft Alvaro Odriozola, t\u00e2n binh tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u Euro mua t\u1eeb Valencia v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 Real Madrid v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3, lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc ti\u1ebfp theo.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady nh\u1ea5t cho hay, Real Madrid s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Eden Hazard, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh gi\u1ea3i Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng B\u1ea1c World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-hazard-dich-than-tuyen-bo-muon-roi-chelsea-172-191203.html\" target=\"_blank\">b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chia tay Chelsea</span> \u0111\u1ec3 \u201c\u0111\u1ed5i gi\u00f3\u201d s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-real-madrid-4-cai-ten-huong-loi-nhat-duoi-thoi-lopetegui-180-191534.html\">G\u00f3c Real Madrid: 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Julen Lopetegui</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-ly-do-tin-tuong-real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-eden-hazard-172-191533.html\">3 l\u00fd do tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Real Madrid s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Eden Hazard</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4368","checkdouble":"191561"},{"date":"08:49 19/07","title":"T\u00e2n binh Odriozola tri \u00e2n HLV Lopetegui trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/19/tan-binh-odriozola-tri-an-hlv-lopetegui-trong-ngay-ra-mat-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Alvaro Odriozola h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a HLV Lopetegui. Anh c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin m\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o m\u00ecnh.</h2><h2>Odriozola h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng Lopetegui</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"http://bongdaplus.vn/alvaro-odriozola-tan-binh-cua-real-madrid-la-ai-2218061807.html\" target=\"_blank\">T\u00e2n binh Odriozola</span> m\u1edbi ra m\u1eaft c\u00e1c C\u0110V Real h\u00f4m qua sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi Real v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed l\u00e0 40 tri\u1ec7u euro. Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real Sociedad n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 35 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i La Liga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu, Odriozola c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng Lopetegui. T\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Real \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn Odriozola v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 thay v\u00ec hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Sergi Roberto v\u00e0 Hector Bellerin.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2n binh Odriozola tri \u00e2n HLV Lopetegui trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2n binh Odriozola tri \u00e2n HLV Lopetegui trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/tan-binh-odriozola-tri-an-hlv-lopetegui-trong-ngay-ra-mat-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Odriozola tri \u00e2n HLV\u00a0Lopetegui trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 HLV Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha sa th\u1ea3i ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Real Madrid. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m Odriozola c\u00f3 suy ngh\u0129 ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c v\u1ec1 HLV Lopetegui.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y bi\u1ebft \u01a1n \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 trao cho t\u00f4i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec b\u00e2y gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y t\u1ea1i Real.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u00e1ng nay. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y mong mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eadt t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB l\u1edbn v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u cao. V\u00ec v\u1eady, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1eddi h\u1ee3t m\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. Lopetegui th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chuy\u00ean gia trong vi\u1ec7c truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Real b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Lopetegui kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng cho m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Real Madrid. Sau khi gi\u00e0nh 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, Zidane \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 kh\u00e1c khi Zidane r\u1eddi Real l\u00e0 si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo c\u0169ng ra \u0111i. Kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Real thay m\u00e1u v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cRonaldo l\u00e0 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng anh \u1ea5y. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. Trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u00fa v\u1ecb\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Real Madrid:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chu-tich-real-madrid-hua-se-no-bom-tan-khoa-lap-ronaldo-180-191561.html\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Real Madrid h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-real-madrid-4-cai-ten-huong-loi-nhat-duoi-thoi-lopetegui-180-191534.html\">G\u00f3c Real Madrid: 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Lopetegui</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4367","checkdouble":"191566"},{"date":"07:13 19/07","title":"Jose Mourinho gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u00e2n binh v\u00f4 danh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/jose-mourinho-giai-thich-ly-do-chieu-mo-tan-binh-vo-danh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Manchester United ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lee Grant t\u1eeb Stoke City theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 v\u00e0 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hai n\u0103m v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 35 tu\u1ed5i.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u00e2n binh v\u00f4 danh</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">MU mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant t\u1eeb Stoke City theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. Anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 ba sau qu\u1ea3 bom t\u1ea5n Fred v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Diogo Dalot, ngay sau khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-chia-tay-johnstone-172-190315.html\" target=\"_blank\">chia tay \u201cc\u00e2y nh\u00e0 l\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1eddn\u201d Sam Johnstones</span> c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Jose Mourinho gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do MU mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Jose Mourinho gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do MU mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/jose-mourinho-giai-thich-ly-do-chieu-mo-tan-binh-vo-danh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19, l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng 35 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd s\u1eafm vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n th\u1ee9 ba d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho David De Gea v\u00e0 Sergio Romero trong khung g\u1ed7 Old Trafford. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong khung g\u1ed7 v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Joel Perreira.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Jose Mourinho l\u1ea1i cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh ra m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 22 tu\u1ed5i, \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1eb7c Bi\u1ec7t l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do Man Utd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u00e2n binh v\u00f4 danh:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i mua Lee Grant b\u1edfi v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. Joel Perreira ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i ch\u01a1i x\u01a1i n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn hai n\u0103m tr\u1eddi \u1edf c\u00e1i tu\u1ed5i 22 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1edbi c\u00f3 Lee, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft t\u1eeb l\u00e2u v\u00e0 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf c\u1ea3 Championship c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Premier League trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Stoke City. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m vai tr\u00f2 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho Joel ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng tin r\u1eb1ng Joel \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y th\u00ec t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em \u0111i m\u01b0\u1ee3n.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-mu-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-thu-mon-lee-grant-172-190317.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/Chinh-thuc-MU-mua-thu-mon-Lee-Grant-chuyen-nhuong-tu-do-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-mu-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-thu-mon-lee-grant-172-190317.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Man Utd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u00e2n binh ai-c\u0169ng-kh\u00f4ng-bi\u1ebft-l\u00e0-ai</span><br>\r\nManchester United ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lee Grant t\u1eeb Stoke City theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do h\u00e8 2018 v\u00e0 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hai n\u0103m v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 35 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4366","checkdouble":"191560"},{"date":"08:40 19/07","title":"T\u00e2n HLV Chelsea: \u201cN\u1ebfu Hazard mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/tan-hlv-chelsea-neu-hazard-muon-ra-di-toi-se-khong-can-duong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Maurizio Sarri v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Eden Hazard v\u00e0 Thibaut Courtois, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay Stamford Bridge \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Hazard v\u00e0 Courtois v\u1ec1 tay Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">World Cup 2018 vinh danh nh\u1eefng Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng B\u1ea1c Eden Hazard hay G\u0103ng Tay V\u00e0ng Thibaut Courtois, nh\u01b0ng ni\u1ec1m vui kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n cho CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Chelsea khi \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1ec1 tay Real Madrid trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-hazard-dich-than-tuyen-bo-muon-roi-chelsea-172-191203.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Hazard tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p</span>, Courtois c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng r\u1eb1ng\u2026 Hazard \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u, anh theo \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 duy\u1ec7t chi \u0111\u1ebfn 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh c\u1ea3 c\u1ee5m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c th\u00e0nh London.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2n HLV Sarri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Hazard kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2n HLV Sarri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Hazard kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/tan-hlv-chelsea-neu-hazard-muon-ra-di-toi-se-khong-can-duong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Hazard v\u00e0 Courtois kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chia tay Chelsea gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sarri s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Hazard ra \u0111i</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0111i \u1edf c\u1ee7a Hazard v\u00e0 Courtois s\u1edbm tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn cho Maurizio Sarri khi c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u1ea5m ch\u1ed7 tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, t\u00e2n HLV 59 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ecf ra lo l\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh m\u1ea5t \u0111i hai ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng ngay khi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Chelsea c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n t\u00f4i l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1eabu HLV h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi n\u00f3, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng pitch v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 th\u1ee9 g\u00ec c\u00f3 trong tay, v\u1eady n\u00ean th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u0103n c\u1ea5m Hazard n\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i v\u00e0 gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi m\u00e0 HLV n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i h\u1ecfi han Hazard trong l\u00fac n\u00e0y khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i sau World Cup. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi nhau m\u1edbi l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 4-5 ng\u00e0y trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t cho Chelsea.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-bo-chelsea-sang-real-madrid-172-191484.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-bo-chelsea-sang-real-madrid.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-bo-chelsea-sang-real-madrid-172-191484.html\">HLV B\u1ec9 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Hazard b\u1ecf Chelsea sang Real Madrid</span><br>\r\nHLV Roberto Martinez khuy\u00ean nh\u1ee7 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng Eden Hazard n\u00ean t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n cho s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 27, thay v\u00ec c\u1ee9 an t\u1ecda \u1edf m\u1ed9t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4365","checkdouble":"191562"},{"date":"08:47 19/07","title":"Ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 Alisson, Klopp \u0111\u00e3 m\u01a1 Liverpool v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/26/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-liverpool-va-cac-danh-hieu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool v\u00e0 tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. V\u1edbi c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 v\u00e0 s\u1eafp c\u00f3 nh\u01b0 Alisson, \u00f4ng hy v\u1ecdng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Liverpool chinh ph\u1ee5c c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Naby Keita, Fabinho v\u00e0 Xherdan Shaqiri. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson c\u0169ng \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Anfield v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Mohamed Salah v\u00e0 Roberto Firmino c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi Liverpool, ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t nh\u1eefng suy \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o t\u1eeb c\u00e1c t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i kh\u00e1c. Nh\u00ecn chung, gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 The Kop m\u00f9a t\u1edbi s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u01a1n m\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Man City cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool v\u00e0 m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool v\u00e0 m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Klopp-phat-bieu-ve-Liverpool-va-mo-vo-doi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Liverpool s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Alisson t\u1eeb Roma</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu 3 m\u00f9a v\u1eeba c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Jurgen Klopp l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 th\u00ec nay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y. Nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n thua ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n nh\u01b0 th\u1eddi gian qua d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nKlopp \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch Premier League b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi West Ham v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 12 th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang gi\u00fap Klopp \u0111\u1ea7y l\u1ea1c quan. \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn 100% nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t\u201d, Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klopp\" title=\"Klopp\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/26/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-liverpool-va-cac-danh-hieu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cLu\u00f4n c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u thay \u0111\u1ed5i, nh\u01b0ng theo c\u1ea3 hai h\u01b0\u1edbng. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, Liverpool ch\u1ec9 \u0111i theo m\u1ed9t h\u01b0\u1edbng. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng tuy\u1ec3n binh, s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch g\u1eafn k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. N\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh c\u00f9ng nhau, b\u1ed5 sung nh\u00e2n l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 \u0111i b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp theo.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Liverpool \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 4 t\u1ea1i Premier League sau Man City, Man United v\u00e0 Tottenham. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft Champions League tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi thua Real Madrid 3-1 b\u1edfi 2 sai l\u1ea7m c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Loris Karius.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-alisson-xac-nhan-roi-roma-toi-liverpool-voi-gia-sieu-khung-172-191549.html\">N\u00f3ng: Alisson x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eddi Roma t\u1edbi Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-o-dau-khi-so-sanh-voi-nhung-thu-mon-hang-dau-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191526.html\">Alisson \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-dung-tien-de-bep-liverpool-vu-alisson-172-191489.html\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p Liverpool v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Brazil</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-khi-xherdan-shaqiri-cap-ben-liverpool-172-191445.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi Xherdan Shaqiri c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Liverpool</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4364","checkdouble":"191567"},{"date":"08:33 19/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Blackburn vs Liverpool 01h45 ng\u00e0y 20/7 (Giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/nhan-dinh-blackburn-vs-liverpool-01h45-ngay-207-giao-huu-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Blackburn vs Liverpool l\u00fac 01h45 ng\u00e0y 20/7 (Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/bla-liv.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span>Blackburn vs Liverpool: 1-3<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch v\u1edbi Blackburn l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu th\u1ee9 4 trong m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Liverpool. Trong 3 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Juergen Klopp ghi b\u00e0n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u1edbi 10 l\u1ea7n l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng sung s\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a The Kop nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u00e0nh h\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi l\u00ean h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Blackburn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLiverpool hi\u1ec7n thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t v\u1eeba d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 (Mignolet, Alexander-Arnold, Henderson, Firmino, Salah, Mane) trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh Shaqiri. D\u00f9 v\u1eady l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong tay Klopp v\u1eabn kh\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi Sturridge, Milner, Van Dijk, Matip, Clyne. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, t\u00e2n binh Fabinho m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Monaco \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil mang \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p cho tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng s\u1eafc s\u1ea3o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Liverpool l\u00e0 Blackburn v\u1eeba gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n l\u00ean ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Championship sau khi \u0111o\u1ea1t ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i League One 2017/18. M\u00e0n l\u00e0m n\u00f3ng trong m\u00f9a H\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Blackburn kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi 1 th\u1eafng, 1 h\u00f2a nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu (Port Vale, Hibernian). Liverpool l\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0o phom. D\u00f9 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Tony Mowbray kh\u00f3 tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nCh\u1eb5n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng<br>\r\nC\u00f3 t\u1edbi 6/10 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y gi\u1eefa Blackburn v\u00e0 Liverpool k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ch\u1eb5n. Hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u0169ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong 5/8 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Blackburn v\u00e0 6/10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Liverpool.</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4363","checkdouble":"191571"},{"date":"08:37 19/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Club America vs MU 09h00 ng\u00e0y 20/7 (Giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/19/nhan-dinh-club-america-vs-mu-09h00-ngay-207-giao-huu-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Club America vs MU l\u00fac 09h00 ng\u00e0y 20/7 (Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-1972018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span>Club America vs MU: 1-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nMan United du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 11 h\u1ea3o th\u1ee7. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. Nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, sau khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u0103ng s\u1ee9c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Romelu Lukaku, Marcus Rashfor, Jesse Lingard\u2026 s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t t\u1edbi 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng l\u1edbn trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Man United. \u0110\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p, HLV Jose Mourinho bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9. Trong danh s\u00e1ch l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f4n l\u00ean t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 James Garner, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 17 tu\u1ed5i. L\u00e0 Tahith Chong, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i U19 M.U. L\u00e0 Mason Greenwood, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 16. \u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ecd x\u00e1t \u1edf chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m nay. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1, Man United c\u00f2n g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1ec1 qu\u00e3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng di chuy\u1ec3n. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Jose Mourinho m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua chuy\u1ebfn bay d\u00e0i v\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0110\u1ea1i T\u00e2y D\u01b0\u01a1ng. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Club America.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n90 ph\u00fat t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Man United trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19. Ch\u01b0a t\u00ednh t\u1edbi y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 suy ki\u1ec7t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00ec di chuy\u1ec3n, ch\u1ec9 ri\u00eang vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi k\u1ebft th\u00fac k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 tr\u1edf ng\u1ea1i v\u1edbi M.U. S\u1ee9c \u1ef3 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man United hi\u1ec7n nay kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn. Ngo\u00e0i ra, vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i ch\u1eafp v\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng nhi\u1ec1u g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1ebb c\u0169ng l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n90 ph\u00fat s\u1eafp t\u1edbi h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi Man United, b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Club America kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 ch\u01a1i. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Mexico. Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi M.U v\u1eeba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n sau k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Club America \u0111\u00e3 quen v\u1edbi c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng. H\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nay, Club America nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 l\u00e9p v\u1ebf so v\u1edbi Man United. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Mexico ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n1 - Trong 4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Man United ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 trung b\u00ecnh m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 0,25 b\u00e0n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN XUNG QUANH<br>\r\n- Club America: Edson Alvarez v\u00e0 Oribe Peralta v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t.<br>\r\n- Man United: Nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t, do \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ngh\u1ec9 th\u00eam sau World Cup.<br>\r\n- Club America th\u1eafng theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1 5/7 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n- Man United thua theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u1ea3 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nT\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 b\u00e0n<br>\r\nTrong 8 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Club America, c\u00f3 6 tr\u1eadn k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf xu\u1ed1ng. 3/5 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Man United c\u0169ng di\u1ec5n ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 tin r\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4362","checkdouble":"191572"},{"date":"05:48 19/07","title":"Arsenal b\u1ecb l\u1eeba ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c khi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ty Trung Qu\u1ed1c?","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/arsenal-bi-lua-ngoan-muc-khi-ky-hop-dong-voi-cong-ty-trung-quoc.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"4361","checkdouble":"191555"},{"date":"06:59 19/07","title":"Neymar l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ee9 hai \u0111\u1ea1t 100 tri\u1ec7u theo d\u00f5i tr\u00ean Instagram","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/19/neymar-la-cau-thu-bong-da-thu-hai-dat-100-trieu-theo-doi-tren-instagram.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00ednh ri\u00eang \u1edf World Cup 2018, ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n Brazil c\u00f3 th\u00eam 10 tri\u1ec7u theo d\u00f5i tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i chuy\u00ean chia s\u1ebb \u1ea3nh v\u00e0 video.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">T\u00ednh ri\u00eang \u1edf World Cup 2018, ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n Brazil c\u00f3 th\u00eam 10 tri\u1ec7u theo d\u00f5i tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i chuy\u00ean chia s\u1ebb \u1ea3nh v\u00e0 video.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNeymar ch\u1ea1m m\u1ed1c 100 tri\u1ec7u theo d\u00f5i h\u00f4m 16/7, ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m C. Ronaldo (135 tri\u1ec7u theo d\u00f5i) trong nh\u00f3m V\u0110V. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 11 trong danh s\u00e1ch t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Instagram \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c theo d\u00f5i nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng t\u00ednh t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n @instagram, Neymar l\u1ecdt top 10 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i do Facebook s\u1edf h\u1eefu n\u00e0y.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Instagram c\u1ee7a Neymar c\u00e1n m\u1ed1c 100 tri\u1ec7u l\u01b0\u1ee3t theo d\u00f5i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Instagram c\u1ee7a Neymar c\u00e1n m\u1ed1c 100 tri\u1ec7u l\u01b0\u1ee3t theo d\u00f5i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/cc-3351-1531904636.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Neymar chia s\u1ebb \u1ea3nh ch\u1ee5p c\u00f9ng con trai Davi Lucca tr\u00ean Instagram. \u1ea2nh: Instagram.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC. Ronaldo ch\u1ea1m m\u1ed1c 100 tri\u1ec7u theo d\u00f5i k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 5/2017. Nh\u1edd c\u00f3 th\u00eam 11 tri\u1ec7u theo d\u00f5i trong th\u1eddi gian World Cup di\u1ec5n ra, anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee9ng sau danh ca Selena Gomez (138 tri\u1ec7u theo d\u00f5i). Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, si\u00eau sao Messi \u0111\u1ee9ng ngay sau v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Neymar, v\u1edbi 97 tri\u1ec7u theo d\u00f5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNeymar thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf World Cup t\u1ea1i Nga, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y ch\u00fa \u00fd b\u1edfi pha \u0103n v\u1ea1 ph\u1ea3n c\u1ea3m trong \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Mexico v\u00f2ng 1/8. T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 pha tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\nAdvertisement<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau ba ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n V\u0110V n\u00e0o g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong top 25. CLB th\u1ec3 thao duy nh\u1ea5t g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong top 25 t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c theo d\u00f5i nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean Instagram l\u00e0 Real Madrid, v\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u l\u01b0\u1ee3t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4360","checkdouble":"191559"},{"date":"18:02 18/07","title":"V\u1eeba t\u1edbi Juve, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/insigne-canh-bao-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cristiano Ronaldo m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1eeb ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Napoli Insigne v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i Serie A.</h2><h2>Ronaldo nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo chia tay Real \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp CLB Juventus trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 105 tri\u1ec7u euro. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u2018B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\u2019 gia t\u0103ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 chinh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec9nh cao Champions League.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Insigne tro lai\" title=\"Insigne tro lai\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/2/8/Nhung-ngoi-sao-co-the-thay-the-Coutinho-tai-Liverpool-hinh-anh-6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Insigne c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Ronaldo v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Serie A</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Ronaldo mang v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd. Tuy nhi\u00ean ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1eeb ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i Serie A v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Italia, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Napoli Lorenzo Insigne cho hay: ''Ch\u00e0o m\u1eebng Ronaldo t\u1edbi Italia, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i t\u00f2 m\u00f2 mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebft anh \u1ea5y th\u00edch \u1ee9ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u1edbi Serie A. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i Italy r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi anh \u1ea5y t\u1eebng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u phi th\u01b0\u1eddng khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Juventus. H\u00e3y ch\u1edd xem trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i''.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m nay, Napoli c\u1ee7a Insigne c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm c\u1ee7a Juventus. V\u1edbi\u00a0vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a HLV Carlo Ancelotti l\u00ean l\u00e0m HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Paolo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm t\u1ea1i Serie A. V\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa Insigne v\u00e0 Ronaldo s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng xem.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cassano-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-messi-180-191515.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/cassano-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-messi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cassano-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-messi-180-191515.html\">N\u1ebfu Ronaldo l\u00e0 Nadal, Messi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Federer</span><br>\r\nCassano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi. C\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Italia d\u00f9ng c\u00e1c huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i qu\u1ea7n v\u1ee3t Rafael Nadal v\u00e0 Roger Federer \u0111\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi hai si\u00eau sao b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/ngoi-sao-ronaldo-ban-moi-tai-san-o-tbn-188-191518.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/ngoi-sao-ronaldo-ban-moi-tai-san-o-tbn.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/hau-truong/ngoi-sao-ronaldo-ban-moi-tai-san-o-tbn-188-191518.html\">Ng\u00f4i sao Ronaldo b\u00e1n m\u1ecdi t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n \u1edf TBN</span><br>\r\nSi\u00eau sao Juventus mu\u1ed1n kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 c\u1ee7a anh \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha, c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi c\u01a1 quan thu\u1ebf v\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0m l\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i Italy.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-chieu-mo-cristiano-ronaldo-co-nhung-gia-tri-con-lon-hon-tien-176-191505.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/juventus-chieu-mo-cristiano-ronaldo-co-nhung-gia-tri-con-lon-hon-tien.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-chieu-mo-cristiano-ronaldo-co-nhung-gia-tri-con-lon-hon-tien-176-191505.html\">Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo: C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u00f2n l\u1edbn h\u01a1n ti\u1ec1n</span><br>\r\n100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i. Vi\u1ec7c Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo nghe t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\n115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4359","checkdouble":"191527"},{"date":"20:12 18/07","title":"Juve s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng v\u1ec1 l\u00e0m b\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/juve-sap-chieu-mo-trung-ve-khung-ve-lam-ban-voi-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi tham v\u1ecdng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, CLB Juventus m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111ang c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Atletico Madrid, Diego Godin \u0111\u1ec3 gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.</h2><h2>CLB Juventus s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Diego Godin</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trung ve Diego Godin\" title=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Diego Godin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/5/26/MU-chi-30-trieu-bang-cho-trung-ve-Diego-Godin-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Diego Godin \u0111\u1ec3 gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 32, Diego Godin ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay t\u1ea1i CLB Atletico Madrid trong su\u1ed1t m\u1ed9t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 qua. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, anh ra s\u00e2n t\u1edbi 45 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn c\u00f9ng Los Rojiblancos\u00a0v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay, CLB Juventus \u0111ang c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mang anh v\u1ec1 Turin. Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Italy, Juventus \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Diego Godin. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italy s\u1ebd d\u00e0nh cho trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Uruguay h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 thua k\u00e9m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Atletico Madrid, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng khi m\u00e0 Juve \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng tham v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 chinh ph\u1ee5c danh hi\u1ec7u Champions League. H\u1ecd v\u1eeba chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 QBV 2017 Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Diego Godin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd \u201cr\u1ebb b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd\u201d, kho\u1ea3ng 18 tri\u1ec7u B\u1ea3ng do trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay c\u00f3 mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Italia \u00a0sinh s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u hay kh\u00f4ng?</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-yeu-to-chi-ra-ronaldo-nen-chon-mu-thay-vi-den-juventus-172-191429.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/1/12/tong-hop-nhung-sieu-pham-ban-thang-cua-ronaldo-khi-con-o-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-yeu-to-chi-ra-ronaldo-nen-chon-mu-thay-vi-den-juventus-172-191429.html\">3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 ch\u1ec9 ra Ronaldo n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn M.U thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus</span><br>\r\nSau 9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i s\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Real, si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Juventus. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin r\u1eb1ng CR7 n\u00ean v\u1ec1 M.U thay v\u00ec...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-chieu-mo-ronaldo-khi-cuoc-song-buoc-phai-co-kich-tinh-176-191424.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/juventus-chieu-mo-ronaldo-khi-cuoc-song-buoc-phai-co-kich-tinh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-chieu-mo-ronaldo-khi-cuoc-song-buoc-phai-co-kich-tinh-176-191424.html\">Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo: Khi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh</span><br>\r\nC\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u nghi ng\u1edd v\u00e0 th\u1eafc m\u1eafc xung quanh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo. Tuy nhi\u00ean, khi \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e1m b\u1ecf t\u1edbi 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro ch\u1ec9 cho m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao, tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-chieu-mo-cristiano-ronaldo-co-nhung-gia-tri-con-lon-hon-tien-176-191505.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/juventus-chieu-mo-cristiano-ronaldo-co-nhung-gia-tri-con-lon-hon-tien.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-chieu-mo-cristiano-ronaldo-co-nhung-gia-tri-con-lon-hon-tien-176-191505.html\">Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo: C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u00f2n l\u1edbn h\u01a1n ti\u1ec1n</span><br>\r\n100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i. Vi\u1ec7c Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo nghe t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4358","checkdouble":"191540"},{"date":"22:06 18/07","title":"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch La Liga ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do Ronaldo chia tay Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/chu-tich-la-liga-tiet-lo-ly-do-ronaldo-chia-tay-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch La Liga, Javier Tebas cho r\u1eb1ng Cristiano Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real Madrid ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 do v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 thu\u1ebf thu nh\u1eadp.\r\n</h2><h2>Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real Madrid v\u00ec thu\u1ebf\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch La Liga ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch La Liga ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/Chu-tich-La-Liga-tiet-lo-ly-do-Ronaldo-roi-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch La Liga cho r\u1eb1ng Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Juventus l\u00e0 v\u00ec thu\u1ebf thu nh\u1eadp</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real Madrid sau 9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1eafn b\u00f3 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha. \u0110\u00edch \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 Juventus, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 7 n\u0103m li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng Ronaldo t\u1edbi Italia \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u2018d\u01b0\u1ee1ng gi\u00e0\u2019 song m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch La Liga, Javier Tebas \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n s\u00e2u xa khi\u1ebfn khi\u1ebfn CR7 \u2018li h\u00f4n\u2019 Real l\u00e0 do li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi thu\u1ebf thu nh\u1eadp. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi t\u1edd\u00a0Mundo Deportivo, \u00f4ng Tebas cho hay: \"Ronaldo ra \u0111i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e0 v\u00ec v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 thu\u1ebf. \u1ede T\u00e2y Ban Nha, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng thu\u1ebf khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Italy. Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n n\u00e0y. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do kh\u00e1c n\u1eefa, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t\"<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 m\u1ed9t t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e0i c\u1ee7a l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 chia tay gi\u1ea3i La Liga song kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Tebas lo ng\u1ea1i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao chia tay gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ed1 1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha. V\u1ecb n\u00e0y n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201cN\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, t\u00f4i lo r\u1eb1ng La Liga c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t 9 ho\u1eb7c 10 ng\u00f4i sao m\u1ed7i k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng thu\u1ebf th\u00ec b\u00e2y gi\u1edd con s\u1ed1 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 3 ho\u1eb7c 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 thu nh\u1eadp tr\u00ean 300 ngh\u00ecn euro/n\u0103m s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed9p 52% ti\u1ec1n thu\u1ebf. T\u1ee9c n\u1ebfu Real ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 30 tri\u1ec7u euro/n\u0103m sau thu\u1ebf cho Ronaldo th\u00ec Los Blancos s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 57,7 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u1ed7i n\u0103m cho CR7. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ee9c thu\u1ebf t\u1ea1i Italia ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 43%.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/juve-sap-chieu-mo-trung-ve-khung-ve-lam-ban-voi-ronaldo-187-191540.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/juve-sap-chieu-mo-trung-ve-khung-ve-lam-ban-voi-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/juve-sap-chieu-mo-trung-ve-khung-ve-lam-ban-voi-ronaldo-187-191540.html\">Juve s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng v\u1ec1 l\u00e0m b\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi tham v\u1ecdng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, CLB Juventus m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111ang c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Atletico Madrid, Diego Godin \u0111\u1ec3 gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cassano-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-messi-180-191515.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/cassano-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-messi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cassano-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-messi-180-191515.html\">N\u1ebfu Ronaldo l\u00e0 Nadal, Messi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Federer</span><br>\r\nCassano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi. C\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Italia d\u00f9ng c\u00e1c huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i qu\u1ea7n v\u1ee3t Rafael Nadal v\u00e0 Roger Federer \u0111\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi hai si\u00eau sao b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/real-madrid-se-song-tot-ma-khong-can-cristiano-ronaldo-421-191509.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/real-madrid-se-song-tot-ma-khong-can-cristiano-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/real-madrid-se-song-tot-ma-khong-can-cristiano-ronaldo-421-191509.html\">Real Madrid s\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng t\u1ed1t m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n Cristiano Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Antonio Cassano ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 khi si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Juventus t\u1eeb Real Madrid trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4357","checkdouble":"191544"},{"date":"23:33 18/07","title":"\u0110\u00e3 xong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/3/4/da-xong-tuong-lai-cua-tien-dao-mauro-icardi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Italia, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t khi m\u00e0 CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Inter Milan \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft chi l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</h2><h2>Inte Milan quy\u1ebft gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi\u00a0ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u00e3 xong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u00e3 xong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/22/Da-xong-tuong-lai-cua-tien-dao-Mauro-Icardi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Inter \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi CLB Real Madrid. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 v\u1eeba qua, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e0m b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3 khi anh \u0111\u00e3 ghi 29 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 trong 34 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u, chi\u1ebfm t\u1edbi 44% t\u1ed5ng pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 Nerazzui c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, Icardi \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 t\u1eeb ph\u00eda CLB Real Madrid, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba chia tay ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 Ronaldo. V\u00ec th\u1ebf Real \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb trung v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n nh\u01b0 ng\u00f4i sao Argentina.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 \u2018ve v\u00e3n\u2019 c\u1ee7a Real, CLB Inter Milan m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i \u2018tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n\u2019 Icardi. Theo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb t\u1edd Gazzetta dello Sport, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan s\u1ebd s\u1edbm g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1993 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn 2023 v\u00e0 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 7,5 \u0111\u1ebfn 8 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a, cao h\u01a1n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 5,5 tri\u1ec7u euro \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t cao t\u1ea1i Serie A. V\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y, Icardi s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao th\u1ee9 2 t\u1ea1i Serie A v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u01b0\u1edbi t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Juventus - Ronaldo v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 30 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. \u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Inter cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Inter t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Champions League.\u00a0<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/juve-sap-chieu-mo-trung-ve-khung-ve-lam-ban-voi-ronaldo-187-191540.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/juve-sap-chieu-mo-trung-ve-khung-ve-lam-ban-voi-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/juve-sap-chieu-mo-trung-ve-khung-ve-lam-ban-voi-ronaldo-187-191540.html\">Juve s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng v\u1ec1 l\u00e0m b\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi tham v\u1ecdng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, CLB Juventus m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111ang c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Atletico Madrid, Diego Godin \u0111\u1ec3 gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-chi-ra-mu-can-chieu-mo-ngay-sao-bu-dt-croatia-421-191381.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/8/2/Ivan-Perisic-noi-gi-truoc-loi-moi-goi-toi-MU-cua-Mourinho--hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-chi-ra-mu-can-chieu-mo-ngay-sao-bu-dt-croatia-421-191381.html\">3 l\u00fd do ch\u1ec9 ra M.U c\u1ea7n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ngay sao b\u1ef1 \u0110T Croatia</span><br>\r\nIvan Perisic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Croatia. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do cho th\u1ea5y M.U c\u1ea7n mua g\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Inter Milan trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-187-real-ra-dieu-kien-de-mu-co-bale-184-191536.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-187-real-ra-dieu-kien-de-mu-co-bale.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-187-real-ra-dieu-kien-de-mu-co-bale-184-191536.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 18/7: Real ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 M.U c\u00f3 Bale</span><br>\r\nReal ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 M.U c\u00f3 Bale, Liverpool s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c, Inter h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Ivan Perisic cho M.U,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c c\u00f3 trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4356","checkdouble":"191546"}]}